config SUN50I_H713_LRADC
	tristate "Allwinner H713 LRADC IIO driver"
	depends on ARCH_SUNXI || COMPILE_TEST
	depends on IIO
	help
	  Say yes here to support the Low-Resolution ADC (LRADC) found in
	  the Allwinner H713 SoC. This driver provides IIO voltage channels
	  for ADC-based keyboard input (via the adc-keys driver) and NTC
	  temperature sensing (via IIO consumer API).

	  This driver replaces direct MMIO access to the LRADC registers,
	  allowing multiple consumers (keyboard + temperature) to share
	  the same hardware safely.

	  To compile this as a module, choose M here: the module will be
	  called sun50i-h713-lradc-iio.
